Please note that you used an older DMP template, from 2022 FWO requests DMPs to follow Flemish Standard DMP template. You can find this template in DMPonline.be, or on the FWO website with more information about their DMP requirements (https://www.fwo.be/en/about-fwo/research-policy/data-management-plan-dmp/). You can copy paste most of the information from the current DMP but there will be some additional questions mainly about data sharing.
